         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <p>Year 2, Payni 22 <note>June 16</note>, Klaudis Drakon ended his life, aged 24 years 3 months and 15 days.</p> 
                   <p> Year 6, Hathyr 25 <note>November 21</note>, 
                    Klaudis Achillas ended  his life, aged 24 years, 2 months and 5 days.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>Payni 22 = June 16 </p>
            <p> Hathyr 25 = November 21</p>
         </div>
         
